ğŸ” Project Overview

This project is an end-to-end data analytics project in Microsoft Excel where raw sales data is transformed into an interactive dashboard to help a retail business analyze performance and make decisions.

The project focuses on analyzing yearly sales data of an online retail store and creating a dashboard report to understand customer behavior, sales trends, and business growth opportunities.

